<%- include('../inc/head') %>

    <div id="container">

        <%- include('../inc/sidebar') %>

            <div id="contents">
                <h3>상점운영정책</h3>
                <ul class="navi">
                    <li class="home"><a href="/" target="_top">홈</a></li>
                    <li>환경설정</li>
                    <li>상점운영정책</li>
                    <li class="on">
                        <%= title %>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <ul class="helpbox">
                    <li>상점운영에 필요한 배송, 교환, 반품등 운영정책을 입력하는 곳입니다.</li>
                    <li>수정을 클릭하시여 내용을 확인하시고 쇼핑몰에 맞는 정책을 기입해 주세요.</li>
                </ul>

                <form name="Frm" method="post">
                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="section_head">
                            <h4><i class="xi-check-circle"></i> 이용약관 수정</h4>
                        </div>

                        <table class="t_form">
                            <caption>이용약관 입력폼</caption>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>제목</th>
                                    <td>
                                        <input type="text" name="subject" class="text_input" style="width:98%;" value="이용약관" readonly="">
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>적용위치</th>
                                    <td>
                                        <input type="text" name="location" class="text_input" style="width:98%;" value="/etc/licensing.do, /order/order_agree.do (비회원구매)">
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>내용</th>
                                    <td>
                                        <textarea class="text_input" style="width:98%;"></textarea>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>

                    <div class="btn_center">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-info">확인</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="cancel()">취소</button>
                    </div>

                </form>


                <%- include('../inc/footer') %>
                    </body>

                    </html>